Package: Nestimate
Title: Network Estimation, Bootstrap, and Temporal Analysis
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Mohammed", "Saqr", email = "saqr@saqr.me", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Comprehensive toolkit for network estimation from sequence and panel data.
    Supports transition networks (relative, frequency, co-occurrence), association
    networks (correlation, partial correlation, graphical lasso, Ising), bootstrap
    inference, permutation testing, higher-order networks (HON, HONEM, HYPA, MOGen),
    GIMME (group iterative multiple model estimation), multi-cluster multi-layer
    networks (MCML), multilevel VAR, graphical VAR, and temporal network analysis
    with time-varying centrality, velocity, and proximity timelines.
